<font size="1"> im so dissapointed. Today so far ive had:

four small cubes of watermelon.
two green grapes.
two doritios.
a cup of milk. [ 90 calories ]
a milkshake. [ 335 calories. ]

and im not sure about the calories in the first three things but ive probably 
had something like 500 calories today. god.
 im going to go exercise and beat the shit out of myself emotionally.
then take a bubble bath and crawl into bed. :[

P.S. fuck milkshakes. i should have checked, i knew it. and i didnt. God damn if i was going to eat that many calories i rather would have actually EATEN something. Why didnt i just get a diet coke...ugh.

<font size="1">so yesterday i think i did okay. Besides what i listed earlier, i had three small chicken strips and a few bites of chinese food. Today so far ive had:

one cup of milk
two small pieces of watermelon
and waterwaterwater
 :]

<font size="1"><b>its 1:50 in the afternoon and so far today all ive had to eat is:

one apple
one animal cracker
one sunchip
a sip of pepsi
a bite of a tuna fish hoagie
and alot of zero calorie gum.

i used livejournal before a long time ago, and now im back to it; because there are some amazing communites on here.
 I use myspace alot more than i use anything else. This will basically be used to keep track of what i eat, and how im doing.
